<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="regret-vt">regret <strong><em>vt</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'ɡret/    美 /rɪ'ɡret/  </p>
<p>(regretted, regretted)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>后悔；懊悔</strong></h4>
<p>to feel sorry about sth you have done ; to wish that  you had not done sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He who will not learn when he is young will regret it when he is old. 
少壮不努力，老大徒伤悲。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>regret doing sth：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He did not regret saying what he did but felt that he could have expressed it differently. 
他并不后悔说出自己做了什么，而是觉得他本来可以换一种表达方式。</p><footer>2009 江苏</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>regret + (that) / wh- 从句：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I regret that I didn’t follow your advice. 
我真后悔没听你的劝告。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>deeply / bitterly / greatly regret</strong> what I said just now.
我对刚才说的话感到非常后悔。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[正式用语] 抱歉；遗憾</strong></h4>
<p>used to say in a formal way that you are sorry about a situation：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is much to be regretted that you can’t join us in the trip. 
你不能和我们一道去旅行，真是遗憾。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>regret + that 从句：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I regret that I will be unable to attend your party.
很遗憾我不能参加你的聚会。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>regret to say / tell / inform ...：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I regret to tell that you didn’t pass the examination.
很遗憾地通知你，你没有通过考试。</p><footer>外研⑥ – 7</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>It’s no use <strong><em>_</em></strong>__ (后悔) what you have done.  （2008 陕西）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. regretting  </p></div>